    // Header
    header#top.header
      div#particles-js
      .text-vertical-center
        h1 Christian Holland
        div#mainSubtitle.tlt Computer Science graduate with experience in developing AI technologies, APIs, web applications and computer games.
        a#FindMoreBtn.button.button-border-primary.button-rounded.js-scroll-trigger(href='#about') Find Out More

        
    // About
    section#about.about
      .container.text-center
        h2 About me
        p.lead
          | I am a young Computer Science major developing Artificial Intelligence technologies during the day and web applications and computer games at night. If you check out my <a class="js-scroll-trigger" href="#services">portfolio</a>, you'll find I have a wide range of skills, along with something to show for each of one. Have a look around - if you like what you see and want to find out more, please drop me an <a class="js-scroll-trigger" href="#contact">email</a>.
        hr
        h2 What have I done since graduating?
        p.lead I graduated from university and went straight into employment as an AI developer for <a id="ebiLink" href="http://ebi.ai/">EBI Solutions</a> on all sorts of interesting AI projects using Node.js and testing frameworks such as Mocha. I mainly created Facebook, Slack and web chat bot API's using <a href="https://www.ibm.com/watson/">IBM Watson</a>, but I also created <a href="https://alexa.amazon.com/">Amazon Alexa</a> Skills and <a href="https://developer.microsoft.com/en-us/windows/kinect">Microsoft Kinect</a> applications using the <a href="https://www.microsoft.com/en-gb/download/details.aspx?id=44561">Kinect SDK</a>.
        p.lead At the start of 2018, I began my travels across the east coast of Australia, broadening my experiences in as many ways possible. I worked as a manual labourer setting up events for <a href="https://www.nofusseventhire.com.au/">No Fuss Event Hire</a>, then moved on to door to door sales for <a href="https://www.thesmithfamily.com.au/">The Smith Family</a>; both within Melbourne over the period of 2 months. After I'd had my fill of Melbourne, I drove to the <a href="http://www.selxnsw.com.au/">SELX</a> cattle yards in Canberra. I worked long hard days for a month, then travelled the rest of the coast up to Cairns. I wanted to get a taste of what more physically demanding jobs were like, and can safely say I'm happy to stick with coding.
          | Upon my return to the UK in July 2018, after a 6 month journey on the other side of the world, I am ready to buckle down and create my legacy through means of code.

          
    // Services
    section#services.services.bg-primary.text-white(data-stellar-background-ratio='0.5')
        .services-container
        .row.text-center
          .col-lg-10.mx-auto
            h2 Cool stuff I've done
            hr.small
            .row
              .col-md-4
                .service-item#si1
                  span.fa-stack.fa-4x
                    i.fa.fa-circle.fa-stack-2x
                    i.fa.fa-cloud.fa-stack-1x.text-primary
                  h4
                    strong IBM Certified Engineer
                  p During my employment at IBM, I achieved a certification acknowledging that I am an IBM Certified Specialist Engineer. Unfortunately, IBM has some technical difficulties with my certification page, so here's a picture of it instead.
                  a#certButton.btn.btn-light(href='../img/cert.jpg') Learn More
              .col-md-4
                .service-item#si2
                  span.fa-stack.fa-4x
                    i.fa.fa-circle.fa-stack-2x
                    i.fa.fa-compass.fa-stack-1x.text-primary
                  h4
                    strong WhoSeddit
                  p WhoSeddit is my final year dissertation project written in Node.js, showing the popularity and spread of rumours across the Twitter platform, using their API.
                  a.btn.btn-light(href='http://bit.ly/2nEUNya') Learn More
              .col-md-4
                .service-item#si3
                  span.fa-stack.fa-4x
                    i.fa.fa-circle.fa-stack-2x
                    i.fa.fa-flask.fa-stack-1x.text-primary
                  h4
                    strong The Hotel
                  p The Hotel is a Three.js project; a horror game written entirely in Javascript. All models and sounds were made by me.
                  a.btn.btn-light(href='http://bit.ly/2hBXC3Q') Learn More
            .row
              .col-md-4
                .service-item#si4
                  span.fa-stack.fa-4x
                    i.fa.fa-circle.fa-stack-2x
                    i.fa.fa-shield.fa-stack-1x.text-primary
                  h4
                    strong Prison Break
                  p Prison Break is a Dying Light custom campaign that a friend and I worked on when the <a id="servLink" href="https://steamdb.info/app/350570/">developers tools</a> first came out. It was done originally just to pass the time, but it blew up in popularity so we decided to finish it.
                  a.btn.btn-light(href='http://bit.ly/2gXaf5q') Learn More
              .col-md-4
                .service-item#si5
                  span.fa-stack.fa-4x
                    i.fa.fa-circle.fa-stack-2x
                    i.fa.fa-shield.fa-stack-1x.text-primary
                  h4
                    strong Advanced Video Editing
                  p I spent a lot of time editing game footage when I was younger. I would have edited real life footage, but at that age I couldn't afford anything that could record in the quality I needed.
                  a.btn.btn-light(href='http://bit.ly/2gxKJTc') Learn More
                  a.btn.btn-light(href='http://bit.ly/2gxKQOC') Learn More
              .col-md-4
                .service-item#si6
                  span.fa-stack.fa-4x
                    i.fa.fa-circle.fa-stack-2x
                    i.fa.fa-shield.fa-stack-1x.text-primary
                  h4
                    strong Music Production
                  p I also spent a lot of time producing music when I was a lot younger. I'm not saying I'm Beethoven... it was just a hobby.
                  a.btn.btn-light(href='http://bit.ly/2hsfx9V') Learn More
        
    // Footer
    section#contact.contact
    footer
      .container
        .row
          .col-lg-10.mx-auto.text-center
            h4
              strong Christian Holland
            hr.small
            ul.list-unstyled
              li
                i.fa.fa-phone.fa-fw
                |                 Please email me for my number
              li
                i.fa.fa-envelope-o.fa-fw
                a(href='mailto:christianoholland@gmail.com') christianoholland@gmail.com
            br
            ul.list-inline
              li.list-inline-item
                a(href='https://www.facebook.com/christian.holland.10')
                  i.fa.fa-facebook.fa-fw.fa-3x
              li.list-inline-item
                a(href='https://www.linkedin.com/in/chris-holland-26644595')
                  i.fa.fa-linkedin.fa-fw.fa-3x
